Reflection Meditation

	Philosophy

		-
			Reflection meditation is to enter into a dialogue with oneself, where one questions
			themselves about their deepest insecurities and answers honestly but without judgement.
		-

	Principles

		Mind Letting

			-
				Mind letting is openly admitting that which one has been repressing or hiding,
				either to themselves, to a projected figure, or privately to someone who can be
				trusted not to disclose it.
			-